data.description: This remarkable property offers a spacious and comfortable living environment, boasting 5 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an inviting basement with an additional entry from outside. Five spacious bedrooms provide ample space for everyone in the family to have their own retreat. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed with comfort and tranquility in mind. Located in the heart of Copiague, this hi-ranch gem is conveniently near schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes. Commuting to nearby cities is a breeze, making this property an ideal choice for those seeking a suburban oasis with easy access to urban amenities. SOLD AS IS!
